{"tid":1816941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"臥底狗的解決辦法","createTime":"2020-01-08T16:05:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T16:22:33.000Z","uid":198684,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c9314ec0d64133b4ebbf8d5f38b0bff2b0d57942","tid":1816941,"uid":198684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:05:06.000Z","msg":"就係打狗救人啊！叫咗半年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家係咪漸漸開始忘卻咗？<br />\n<br />\n發夢 <br />\n<br />\n根本唔需要刻意捉鬼。<br />\n<br />\n因為「鬼」到最後一定會現身捉人<br />\n<br />\n「鬼」現真身係幾時？<br />\n<br />\n就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">收網捉人</span></span>既時候<br />\n<br />\n以今晚TKO為例，臨尾幾條臥底狗衝入人群咁都被佢哋扯<br />\n<br />\n走兩位手足。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「鬼」一現身就組隊打波，唔夠膽打波就麻煩唔好再捉<br />\n<br />\n捉鬼敢死隊捉完隻「鬼」都要處理佢㗎，口屌完就放生只<br />\n<br />\n會放虎歸山"},{"pid":"645490469833f04625a6137b2e31ba2add66ad5a","tid":1816941,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:07:36.000Z","msg":"勇武都唔夠人"},{"pid":"4c97c84c9083cd8944e2fee22c644d4c761a9354","tid":1816941,"uid":198684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"645490469833f04625a6137b2e31ba2add66ad5a","tid":1816941,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:07:36.000Z","msg":"勇武都唔夠人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:11:49.000Z","msg":"點分和勇，夠膽捉鬼仲唔夠勇？ 如果唔夠勇就唔好亂捉<br />\n<br />\n組隊打波人人做得到<br />\n<br />\n再唔係開遮都已經好夠<br />\n<br />\n7-8月第一次發現臥底狗係被和理非鬧走咋，冇人被咬<br />\n<br />\n依家大家退化咗定咩"},{"pid":"03b62688b5975249d8aeccd39a092a187d3a8e44","tid":1816941,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:22:33.000Z","msg":"捉鬼個班<br />\n<br />\n唔該<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">隻鬼現形既時候先捉鬼</span></span>，救手足"}]}